lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌佢地老母，最撚黑人憎一定係2邊都有刀鋒，一開始佢地食左藍，之後人地刀鋒一早lv4出來殺左人，就會懶鳩我話<span style=\"color: red;\">刀鋒差距</span>，我距你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上唔到4LV既話，我就會係中路食兵"},{"pid":"6ba9d5d3bee085a883b3d979c5f399840c58231c","tid":97513,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"單挑玩左100場剩輸左8場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a391d3efe66e623284638f1511195c43d21c1366","tid":97513,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單挑玩左100場剩輸左8場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9684bdd41a86ce0dcff54590ddcf9f6b5b7936e0","tid":97513,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"Jas.C<br />\n<br />\n加我打雙排"},{"pid":"c319abcd359e0f1d88fcce7c58c9fd1875137cce","tid":97513,"uid":39902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1e10d1c2a5f3436869f5aa8db924cca6c609f15","tid":97513,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:39:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a78066a3a07d96682897089434ad0f1de7fcf479","tid":97513,"uid":67765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:41:03.000Z","msg":"有冇香港嘅團，得C排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3543174491675c0f1b23ed7d21b4387c0a057199","tid":97513,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁大怨氣既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我完全明白，有時d人真係好on9，我用刀鋒，佢地一開始就打走隻藍，之後人地刺客就lv4去龍路搞人，我仲lv3無大技，去到都幫唔到手咩手，叫龜d又唔理，係都要衝，俾人殺左又懶鳩我，又完全無食龍概念，自己又唔諗下俾人殺左人地同我有等差，一直團戰送死但又繼續衝，死左又懶鳩我廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次佢地死左我就要去幫佢地守塔清兵，跟住明明唔夠打佢地又喺另一邊開戰，我完全無時間做下自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 團戰又唔睇下地圖同人數，有時a喺上路，基本可以偷襲佢地，叫又唔聽，係咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌佢地老母，最撚黑人憎一定係2邊都有刀鋒，一開始佢地食左藍，之後人地刀鋒一早lv4出來殺左人，就會懶鳩我話<span style=\"color: red;\">刀鋒差距</span>，我距你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上唔到4LV既話，我就會係中路食兵</blockquote><br />\n重點唔係邊度食兵，係刀鋒一定要最快時間上lv4，一開始打紅，叫人幫手集合打幾下都唔肯，你幫打幾下已經可以快對面好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n街場太多ON9仔, 上唔到4LV, 我就一定會搶佢地經濟<br />\nD ON9仔 唔幫打都算 唔睇草比人屠真係想直接投"},{"pid":"e7b65e763bcee0d9f60202be97558d076b9ca3cc","tid":97513,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:42:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b5f73679d9e1d937c6fc79e8c8d61040f889e5d","tid":97513,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:42:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>單挑玩左100場剩輸左8場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n單挑我用渥馬，夠呂布做，不過唔夠金納做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單挑我用呂布 好多人打完之後就話單挑用什麼呂布"},{"pid":"58e6d5e2c9c0cc881d258ebaede13e0e24d483ef","tid":97513,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:44:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a7b9548313d1ad7f69ff6c0fdd11e4e5d181fc3","tid":97513,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上唔到4LV既話，我就會係中路食兵</blockquote><br />\n重點唔係邊度食兵，係刀鋒一定要最快時間上lv4，一開始打紅，叫人幫手集合打幾下都唔肯，你幫打幾下已經可以快對面好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n街場太多ON9仔, 上唔到4LV, 我就一定會搶佢地經濟<br />\nD ON9仔 唔幫打都算 唔睇草比人屠真係想直接投</blockquote><br />\n係啊，有時點一下想人睇水，無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係刺客的話，一定幫睇水先，如果同路會幫手打幾下立即上路，費時搶走經驗值</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過見到低牌位木牌秒鎖刀峰 我就會搶佢經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35c5bf053db0796642ae066925e0e636c074c8b","tid":97513,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d92cacea13818dda7180f6cd7b721d2165b6ced9","tid":97513,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e136cfd11ea6f2f9aa8b419cf6400c0c1f611508","tid":97513,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n街場太多ON9仔, 上唔到4LV, 我就一定會搶佢地經濟<br />\nD ON9仔 唔幫打都算 唔睇草比人屠真係想直接投</blockquote><br />\n係啊，有時點一下想人睇水，無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係刺客的話，一定幫睇水先，如果同路會幫手打幾下立即上路，費時搶走經驗值</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過見到低牌位木牌秒鎖刀峰 我就會搶佢經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我地雙排啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nY2H 玩刀鋒<br />\n納克螺絲 玩渥馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加左你 不過好似排唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a9caca1f27fd1170133c315a47468cf3754f8f","tid":97513,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a78f91a97a9983510cb1ae3749449e6db613812f","tid":97513,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過見到低牌位木牌秒鎖刀峰 我就會搶佢經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我地雙排啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nY2H 玩刀鋒<br />\n納克螺絲 玩渥馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加左你 不過好似排唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我2個都係c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> s1玩到a3同a1，單排點升都升唔s，好撚嬲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要有決心一個打哂對面全部人, 冇野做就食兵推塔 唔好浪費每一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc22779e7e6f92b7472a859b43d86cbd598a7bf1","tid":97513,"uid":57580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"有興趣<br />\nIs:月美等出良"},{"pid":"a73c69240130972737784c984404f5d9a5665ccc","tid":97513,"uid":57580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有興趣<br />\nI<span style=\"color: red;\">d</span>:月美等出良</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fa484a44f00bc5794bb56864c7570991e4c88ef8","tid":97513,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有興趣<br />\nI<span style=\"color: red;\">d</span>:月美等出良</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加左你"},{"pid":"189d93196ef1df317bee4d8927efdbeed7cc7b0b","tid":97513,"uid":53136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲死台仔真係好撚廢，場場雷<br />\n<br />\n操作屎唔緊要，問題係冇觀念。玩到b牌，啲坦英仲係死要出攻裝 以為自己一騎當千。一個衝入入地成隊人度想執個殘血頭，一人一招控技你都含撚啦<br />\n<br />\n都算，應退唔退，死要追追追追，戇鳩仔淨係識殺人。唔識得些好意須回手，殺完人兩個叫撚咗走，係要追鳩啲坦，俾人拖到復活減曬全隊。我識判斷形勢知邊啲有得打邊啲唔夠做，你啲傻鳩追人我梗係唔撚跟，之後就問我去咗邊。話我廢？我場撚場mvp呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/01/183524_8183029522ff5068c8be50286c38542d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F01%2F1